{
  "video_id": "K8x9x1G6Sa8",
  "title": "Episode 4.1: An Introduction to Negligence",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2569.0,
      "end_time": 4571.0,
      "text": ">> Episode 4.1."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4571.0,
      "end_time": 7474.0,
      "text": "\"Overview of Negligence.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7474.0,
      "end_time": 9242.0,
      "text": "This episode provides an overview"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9242.0,
      "end_time": 11578.0,
      "text": "of the negligence cause of action"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11578.0,
      "end_time": 15347.0,
      "text": "and compares it to intentional tort liability."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15348.0,
      "end_time": 19519.0,
      "text": "Remember that there are three main types of tort liability."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19519.0,
      "end_time": 25224.0,
      "text": "Intentional torts, negligence, and strict liability."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25225.0,
      "end_time": 29396.0,
      "text": "Intentional tort is not a cause of action in itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29396.0,
      "end_time": 31765.0,
      "text": "Instead, it is a category made up"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31765.0,
      "end_time": 34134.0,
      "text": "of multiple causes of action"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34134.0,
      "end_time": 37700.0,
      "text": "including battery, assault,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37700.0,
      "end_time": 42142.0,
      "text": "false imprisonment, trespass, conversion, et cetera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42142.0,
      "end_time": 45645.0,
      "text": "each with its own prima facie case."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45645.0,
      "end_time": 49150.0,
      "text": "And strict liability is also an umbrella term"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49150.0,
      "end_time": 52118.0,
      "text": "used to describe a few exceptional situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52118.0,
      "end_time": 54821.0,
      "text": "where the law assigns liability to the defendant"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54821.0,
      "end_time": 57390.0,
      "text": "even where the harm was caused by accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57390.0,
      "end_time": 59250.0,
      "text": "unlike intentional torts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59250.0,
      "end_time": 63495.0,
      "text": "and even where the defendant was careful, unlike negligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63496.0,
      "end_time": 66166.0,
      "text": "Negligence works differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66166.0,
      "end_time": 69768.0,
      "text": "Most jurisdictions treat it as a single cause of action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69769.0,
      "end_time": 72739.0,
      "text": "not a category or umbrella term."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73840.0,
      "end_time": 76420.0,
      "text": "The prima facie case of negligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76420.0,
      "end_time": 78144.0,
      "text": "is made up of four elements--"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78144.0,
      "end_time": 83983.0,
      "text": "duty, breach, causation, and damages."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83983.0,
      "end_time": 89656.0,
      "text": "First, the defendant must have owed a duty to the plaintiff."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89656.0,
      "end_time": 93660.0,
      "text": "Second, the defendant must have breached that duty"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93660.0,
      "end_time": 96996.0,
      "text": "by failing to exercise due care."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96996.0,
      "end_time": 101234.0,
      "text": "Third, the defendant&#39;s breach must have been the actual"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101234.0,
      "end_time": 105710.0,
      "text": "and proximate cause of the plaintiff&#39;s injuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105710.0,
      "end_time": 109709.0,
      "text": "And fourth, the plaintiff must have suffered actual harm"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109709.0,
      "end_time": 112479.0,
      "text": "to person or property."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112479.0,
      "end_time": 116820.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s compare intentional torts and negligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 116820.0,
      "end_time": 117984.0,
      "text": "in more detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117984.0,
      "end_time": 121521.0,
      "text": "Unlike strict liability, intentional torts and negligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121521.0,
      "end_time": 124123.0,
      "text": "are both based on fault,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124123.0,
      "end_time": 128194.0,
      "text": "but fault is established in many different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128193.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130229.00000000001,
      "text": "We talked about several intentional tort"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130229.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131464.0,
      "text": "causes of action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131464.0,
      "end_time": 134000.0,
      "text": "but the basic idea behind all of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134000.0,
      "end_time": 136603.0,
      "text": "whether we&#39;re talking about battery or trespass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136603.0,
      "end_time": 138671.0,
      "text": "false imprisonment or assault,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138671.0,
      "end_time": 141908.0,
      "text": "is that the defendant is liable for a deliberate"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141908.0,
      "end_time": 144911.0,
      "text": "or intentional invasion of the plaintiff&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144911.0,
      "end_time": 147347.0,
      "text": "legally protected interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147347.0,
      "end_time": 151284.0,
      "text": "The defendant&#39;s volitional act with intent"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151284.0,
      "end_time": 152852.0,
      "text": "to cause an invasion of the plaintiff&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152852.0,
      "end_time": 154821.0,
      "text": "legally protected interest"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154821.0,
      "end_time": 157490.0,
      "text": "is what makes her conduct wrongful"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157490.0,
      "end_time": 160460.0,
      "text": "in the case of intentional torts."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 160460.0,
      "end_time": 162795.0,
      "text": "Negligence law is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 162795.0,
      "end_time": 166432.0,
      "text": "The defendant is liable for an unreasonable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 166432.0,
      "end_time": 171170.0,
      "text": "but not deliberate, invasion of the plaintiff&#39;s interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171170.0,
      "end_time": 173572.0,
      "text": "The duty and breach elements combined"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 173573.0,
      "end_time": 177277.0,
      "text": "are what makes the defendant&#39;s conduct wrongful."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 177277.0,
      "end_time": 181214.0,
      "text": "Under the duty element, the plaintiff must show"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181214.0,
      "end_time": 183416.0,
      "text": "that the defendant owed a duty to the plaintiff"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183416.0,
      "end_time": 185151.0,
      "text": "to be careful."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185151.0,
      "end_time": 188221.0,
      "text": "In most negligence cases, the duty element"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188221.0,
      "end_time": 191570.0,
      "text": "is easily established by the plaintiff."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 191570.0,
      "end_time": 193326.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because in cases where the defendant"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 193326.0,
      "end_time": 196796.0,
      "text": "is engaged in some kind of affirmative activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 196796.0,
      "end_time": 200533.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s driving a car or operating a chemical plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 200533.0,
      "end_time": 203690.0,
      "text": "the general rule is that she owes a duty"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 203690.0,
      "end_time": 206905.0,
      "text": "to conduct that activity with reasonable care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 206906.0,
      "end_time": 210143.0,
      "text": "so as to avoid causing foreseeable injury"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210143.0,
      "end_time": 213112.0,
      "text": "to other people or their property."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 213112.0,
      "end_time": 216849.0,
      "text": "Under the breach element, the plaintiff must show"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216849.0,
      "end_time": 219452.0,
      "text": "that the defendant breached the duty to be careful."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219452.0,
      "end_time": 222388.0,
      "text": "Or in other words, that the defendant&#39;s conduct"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 222388.0,
      "end_time": 224791.0,
      "text": "fell below the standard of care required"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 224791.0,
      "end_time": 227393.0,
      "text": "under the circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 227393.0,
      "end_time": 231164.0,
      "text": "Note that the breach required for negligence liability"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 231164.0,
      "end_time": 234333.0,
      "text": "is considerably broader than the act required"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 234334.0,
      "end_time": 236869.0,
      "text": "for intentional tort liability."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 236869.0,
      "end_time": 240273.0,
      "text": "For one thing, negligence liability can be based"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240273.0,
      "end_time": 243142.0,
      "text": "on a non-volitional act."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 243142.0,
      "end_time": 245945.0,
      "text": "For example, if I fall asleep while driving"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245945.0,
      "end_time": 248180.0,
      "text": "and hit a pedestrian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 248181.0,
      "end_time": 250817.0,
      "text": "I would probably be liable for negligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250817.0,
      "end_time": 252585.0,
      "text": "but not for battery."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252585.0,
      "end_time": 254854.0,
      "text": "There would be no liability for battery"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 254854.0,
      "end_time": 256522.0,
      "text": "because when I got behind the wheel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 256522.0,
      "end_time": 258925.0,
      "text": "I did not intend to hurt anyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 258925.0,
      "end_time": 261160.0,
      "text": "nor did I act with substantial certainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263429.0,
      "text": "that someone would be hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 263429.0,
      "end_time": 265998.0,
      "text": "But there would be liability for negligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 265999.0,
      "end_time": 270360.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s careless to fall asleep while driving."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270360.0,
      "end_time": 272605.0,
      "text": "Also, under certain circumstances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 272605.0,
      "end_time": 275842.0,
      "text": "an omission can be the basis of negligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 275842.0,
      "end_time": 278277.0,
      "text": "whereas an omission is rarely the basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 278277.0,
      "end_time": 280680.0,
      "text": "of an intentional tort."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 280680.0,
      "end_time": 283716.0,
      "text": "For example, if I operate a driving range"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283716.0,
      "end_time": 286452.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s located next to a jogging path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 286452.0,
      "end_time": 288388.0,
      "text": "I might be negligent for failing to erect"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 288388.0,
      "end_time": 290522.0,
      "text": "a sufficiently high fence or net"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290523.0,
      "end_time": 293526.0,
      "text": "to keep golf balls from hitting joggers."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293526.0,
      "end_time": 297630.0,
      "text": "I owe a duty to operate my driving range with due care"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 297630.0,
      "end_time": 300133.0,
      "text": "and I owe that duty to anyone who might"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 300133.0,
      "end_time": 304169.0,
      "text": "foreseeably be harmed if I am not careful."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 304170.0,
      "end_time": 307106.0,
      "text": "My failure to erect a barrier between the driving range"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 307106.0,
      "end_time": 309375.0,
      "text": "and the jogging path probably amounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 309375.0,
      "end_time": 311844.0,
      "text": "to a breach of my duty."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 311844.0,
      "end_time": 315882.0,
      "text": "Together, duty and breach establish the wrongfulness"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 315882.0,
      "end_time": 319352.0,
      "text": "of the defendant&#39;s conduct, taking the place of intent"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 319352.0,
      "end_time": 321654.0,
      "text": "in establishing fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 322655.0,
      "end_time": 325857.0,
      "text": "Another difference between negligence and intentional torts"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 325858.0,
      "end_time": 329362.0,
      "text": "is that the law of intentional torts protects interests"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 329362.0,
      "end_time": 332665.0,
      "text": "that go beyond being free from actual physical harm"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 332665.0,
      "end_time": 334767.0,
      "text": "or property damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 334767.0,
      "end_time": 337469.0,
      "text": "Even if it is only the plaintiff&#39;s feelings"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 337470.0,
      "end_time": 339872.0,
      "text": "or sense of dignity that&#39;s hurt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 339872.0,
      "end_time": 342800.0,
      "text": "that can be sufficient for purposes"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 342800.0,
      "end_time": 344977.0,
      "text": "of intentional tort liability."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 344977.0,
      "end_time": 347179.0,
      "text": "If I spit in your face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 347180.0,
      "end_time": 349449.0,
      "text": "you might not be physically injured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 349449.0,
      "end_time": 352510.0,
      "text": "but I could be liable for battery nonetheless"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 352510.0,
      "end_time": 355621.0,
      "text": "because the contact offends your dignity."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 355621.0,
      "end_time": 357623.0,
      "text": "Negligence is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 357623.0,
      "end_time": 361600.0,
      "text": "The plaintiff generally must show actual harm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 361600.0,
      "end_time": 363563.0,
      "text": "also referred to as \"damages,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 363563.0,
      "end_time": 367265.0,
      "text": "in the form of personal injury or property damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 367266.0,
      "end_time": 370269.0,
      "text": "Emotional harm or harm to dignity alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 370269.0,
      "end_time": 374707.0,
      "text": "are generally insufficient for negligence liability."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 374707.0,
      "end_time": 378945.0,
      "text": "If I carelessly cause spit to fall onto your face"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 378945.0,
      "end_time": 381314.0,
      "text": "without deliberately making it happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 381314.0,
      "end_time": 383683.0,
      "text": "I would only be liable for negligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 383683.0,
      "end_time": 388221.0,
      "text": "if you can show that you were actually injured in some way."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 388221.0,
      "end_time": 391457.0,
      "text": "Perhaps because you developed an eye infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 392959.0,
      "end_time": 395361.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also important to note that intentional torts"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 395361.0,
      "end_time": 399599.0,
      "text": "and negligence are subject to distinct defenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 399599.0,
      "end_time": 402335.0,
      "text": "The various privileges for intentional torts--"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 402335.0,
      "end_time": 405505.0,
      "text": "consent, self-defense, defense of others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 405505.0,
      "end_time": 408107.0,
      "text": "defense of property, private necessity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 408107.0,
      "end_time": 414800.0,
      "text": "and public necessity-- do not apply to negligence liability."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 414800.0,
      "end_time": 417349.0,
      "text": "The two affirmative defenses to a claim of negligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 417350.0,
      "end_time": 420753.0,
      "text": "are assumption of risk, which is somewhat similar"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 420753.0,
      "end_time": 424323.0,
      "text": "to the consent defense to intentional torts..."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 424323.0,
      "end_time": 427659.0,
      "text": "and contributory or comparative negligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 427660.0,
      "end_time": 428995.0,
      "text": "which is based on the argument"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 428995.0,
      "end_time": 431631.0,
      "text": "that the plaintiff&#39;s own negligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 431631.0,
      "end_time": 433198.0,
      "text": "contributed to his injuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 433199.0,
      "end_time": 435868.0,
      "text": "and thus, his recovery of damages should be reduced"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 435868.0,
      "end_time": 438838.0,
      "text": "or even barred altogether."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 438838.0,
      "end_time": 440907.0,
      "text": "Before we delve into negligence law"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 440907.0,
      "end_time": 442674.0,
      "text": "in the episodes that follow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 442675.0,
      "end_time": 445311.0,
      "text": "there are two key concepts that are important"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 445311.0,
      "end_time": 447280.0,
      "text": "to highlight at this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 447280.0,
      "end_time": 450782.0,
      "text": "Reasonableness and foreseeability."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 450783.0,
      "end_time": 453619.0,
      "text": "You may have already noticed that these two concepts"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 453619.0,
      "end_time": 455888.0,
      "text": "come up again and again in the various elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 455888.0,
      "end_time": 459625.0,
      "text": "of the prima facie case and affirmative defenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459625.0,
      "end_time": 461894.0,
      "text": "You may also have noticed that unreasonableness"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 461894.0,
      "end_time": 465364.0,
      "text": "and foreseeability are related to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 465364.0,
      "end_time": 468334.0,
      "text": "Whether an act or omission is unreasonable--"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 468334.0,
      "end_time": 470169.0,
      "text": "and thus amounts to a breach of the duty"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 470169.0,
      "end_time": 472671.0,
      "text": "to be careful, for example--"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 472672.0,
      "end_time": 474974.0,
      "text": "depends partly on whether or not you might be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 474974.0,
      "end_time": 478440.0,
      "text": "to foresee that harm would occur as a result"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 478440.0,
      "end_time": 480613.0,
      "text": "of the act or omission."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 480613.0,
      "end_time": 483816.0,
      "text": "And the test for foreseeability begs the question"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 483816.0,
      "end_time": 487486.0,
      "text": "of who might be able to foresee harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 487486.0,
      "end_time": 491557.0,
      "text": "And the answer is a reasonable person."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 491557.0,
      "end_time": 494160.0,
      "text": "So foreseeability is sometimes referred to"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 494160.0,
      "end_time": 497797.0,
      "text": "as \"reasonable foreseeability.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 497797.0,
      "end_time": 501670.0,
      "text": "Both of these concepts are sort of slippery."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 501670.0,
      "end_time": 503936.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t provide much in the way of a bright line rule"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 503936.0,
      "end_time": 507600.0,
      "text": "that makes it easy to say, \"Yes, that&#39;s reasonable,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 507600.0,
      "end_time": 509241.0,
      "text": "or \"No, that&#39;s unreasonable.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 509242.0,
      "end_time": 513412.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, that&#39;s foreseeable,\" or \"No, that&#39;s unforeseeable.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 513412.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517950.00000000006,
      "text": "Making these determinations is often left to the jury."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 517950.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522355.00000000006,
      "text": "In close cases, the point isn&#39;t so much to know the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 522355.0,
      "end_time": 524223.0,
      "text": "to be able to predict with certainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 524222.0,
      "end_time": 526726.0,
      "text": "whether this or that will be deemed reasonable"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 526726.0,
      "end_time": 528940.0,
      "text": "or foreseeable."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 528940.0,
      "end_time": 530596.0,
      "text": "The point is to learn how to make the arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 530596.0,
      "end_time": 532365.0,
      "text": "on both sides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 532365.0,
      "end_time": 535268.0,
      "text": "and especially how to frame those arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 535268.0,
      "end_time": 538371.0,
      "text": "in terms of the relevant legal principles."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 538371.0,
      "end_time": 541240.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll return to these two concepts repeatedly"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 541240.0,
      "end_time": 543309.0,
      "text": "in the episodes that follow."
    }
  ]
}